Package: MMPCA
Type: Package
Title: Inference and Clustering for Mixture of Multinomial PCA
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Nicolas Jouvin
Maintainer: Nicolas Jouvin <nicolas.jouvin@univ-paris1.fr>
Description: Cluster any count data matrix in the format of a 
    DocumentTermMatrix. Currently only the banch and bound C-VEM is implemented. 
    But soon the simple greedy procedures will be added.  
